game:medieval-quickstart-text:
Medieval Fashion

The intention of this mod is to inrease the medieval style decorations.
Recipes, blocks, containers, clothing, weapons, tools, fuels, items, and textures have been added.
Some drops and recipes have been modified to make life in Vintage Story easier, but these modifications are not over the top.
¡I hope you enjoy this mod!

I want to thank my friend Mister_Andy_Dandy for his fabulous mod, my friend CATASTEROID and SpearAndFang for their help and ideas, and my friend macoto_hino for the Japanese translation.
